+): (ma: Either<L, R>) => Either<L2, R>
+
+matchMEither<L, R, A>(
+  onLeft: (l: L) => A | Promise<A>,
+  onRight: (r: R) => A | Promise<A>
+): (ma: Either<L, R>) => Promise<A>
+```
+
+### Result
+
+Result-specific bifunctor monad implementation:
+
+```typescript
