+## Terminal Fold Operations
+
+### `.reduce(reducer, initial)`
+
+Reduces all values to a single result.
+
+**Signature:**
+```typescript
+reduce<R>(reducer: (acc: R, value: A) => R, initial: R): Promise<R>
+```
+
+**Example:**
+```typescript
