+// Result: true (vacuous truth)
+
+const emptyAny = emptyTraversal.any(n => n > 0)(numbers);
+// Result: false
+```
+
+### Single Element
+```typescript
+const singleElement = [42];
+
+const singleReduce = eachTraversal.reduce((sum, n) => sum + n, 0)(singleElement);
